One of my favorite animes, and probably the best multi-movie package I've ever bought. The first movie is by far the best in the collection, but the other 2 are very close to that caliber. I have noticed the 2nd movie recycled some scenes from the 1st, but reskinned them to match the context of the scene. Not really anything I'd say hurt the quality, just kind of a weird decision.
